resp_sed_epi: respiration rate of epilimnetic sediments (parameter no longer used in model)
c_w: Fitting coefficient for light extinction in water
c_poc_r: Fitting coefficient for light extinction of recalcitrant POC
c_poc_l: Fitting coefficient for light extinction of labile POC
c_doc_r: Fitting coefficient for light extinction of recalcitrant DOC
c_doc_l: Fitting coefficient for light extinction of labile DOC
ice_transmit: Coefficient for percent of light transmitted through ice
c_npp_split: Ratio of DOC to POC production from NPP
k_winter_adjust: Atmospheric gas exchange adjustmenet during ice covered conditions
k_pocr_epi: Piston velocity settling rate of epilimnetic recalcitrant POC
k_pocl_epi: Piston velocity settling rate of epilimnetic labile POC
k_pocr_hypo: Piston velocity settling rate of hypolimnetic recalcitrant POC
k_pocl_hypo: Piston velocity settling rate of hypolimnetic labile POC
albedo: percentage of short wave radiation reflected off of lake surface
